---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="问题反馈 - V2er">
  <!-- 简化的导航栏 -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 backdrop-blur-lg bg-black/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-24">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-4 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
          <img
            src="/favicon-dark.svg"
            alt="V2er Logo"
            class="h-12 w-12"
          >
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-extrabold text-2xl tracking-tight font-['Inter']" style="color: #F5F5F5">
              V2er
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-medium tracking-wide">
              优雅的 V2EX 客户端
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a
          href="/"
          class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300
                 transition-all duration-300 ease-out rounded-lg
                 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i>
          返回首页
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-24 pb-16 px-4">
    <!-- 背景渐变 -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- 标题区域 -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight">
          <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400">
            问题反馈
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          GitHub Issues 是我们唯一的问题反馈渠道。<br class="hidden sm:inline">
          请根据您使用的平台选择对应的入口提交问题。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 平台卡片 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <!-- Android 卡片 -->
        <a
          href="https://github.com/v2er-app/Android/issues/new"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="group p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-zinc-800
                 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/[0.06]
                 hover:border-zinc-600 hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/20 to-green-600/20
                        flex items-center justify-center mb-6
                        group-hover:from-green-500/30 group-hover:to-green-600/30 transition-all">
              <i class="fab fa-android text-4xl text-green-400"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Android</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
              提交 Android 版本相关的问题或建议
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl
                         bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 font-medium
                         group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-all">
              <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
              提交 Issue
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm opacity-0 -translate-x-2
                        group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all"></i>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- iOS 卡片 -->
        <a
          href="https://github.com/v2er-app/iOS/issues/new"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="group p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-zinc-800
                 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/[0.06]
                 hover:border-zinc-600 hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-purple-600/20
                        flex items-center justify-center mb-6
                        group-hover:from-blue-500/30 group-hover:to-purple-600/30 transition-all">
              <i class="fab fa-apple text-4xl text-white"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">iOS</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
              提交 iOS 版本相关的问题或建议
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl
                         bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 font-medium
                         group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-all">
              <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
              提交 Issue
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm opacity-0 -translate-x-2
                        group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all"></i>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 警告提示 -->
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/30 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-orange-300 flex items-center gap-3">
          <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-orange-400"></i>
          <span>请勿在 App Store 或 Google Play 评论区反馈问题，我们无法在商店中回复或跟进。</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 提示信息 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-zinc-800/50">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-500"></i>
          提交高质量 Issue 的建议
        </h3>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500/70 mt-1 text-xs"></i>
            <span>描述问题时请包含具体的操作步骤</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500/70 mt-1 text-xs"></i>
            <span>提供您的设备型号和系统版本</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500/70 mt-1 text-xs"></i>
            <span>如有可能，请附上截图或录屏</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500/70 mt-1 text-xs"></i>
            <span>提交前请先搜索是否已有相同问题</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
